The second China International Consumer Products Expo, which is currently underway at Haikou in Hainan, has once again reiterated China's determination to further open up to the world. CGTN's Michelle Van Den Bergh spoke to Norman Sze, Vice Chair of Deloitte China to understand his views on how companies can make use of the opportunities arising from China's high-level opening-up and the development of the Hainan free trade port.